title: Filet of Fish
ingredients: Frozen breaded Pollock **(or other white fish)** patty
steps: Put fish filet(s) in the oven according to manufacturer's instructions
When there are about 5 minutes left, griddle the bun with a little butter
Once fish is done, put cheese **(if using)** on top of cooling filets to melt
Once buns are cool, top with tartar sauce
notes: Quick and easy meal that brings back those friday McDonald's memories
